The main goal of the program will be to make the time spent by a person at a computer safer for his body by directly affecting his work and rest (reducing the brightness of the screen with a change in the time of day, automatically pausing the video during a long viewing in order to take a person out of “focus” and remind him of the necessary rest for the eyes, a suggestion to switch to reading mode when studying huge texts, etc.) and indirect (useful tips on changing the screen settings and your real workplace).
The disadvantage of the program is that over time it can get boring and a person will want to turn it off. 
To solve this problem, the user will be able to choose the “degree of control” he needs, this parameter will affect the capabilities of the program and the frequency of its actions.
